System class belongs to the lang package. All the methods of the system class are static. Hence all the methods
of the System class can be called in any program using
"System.exit(1)" OR "System.gc()" format.

Some of the important methods are menthioned in the System class. Please go through the Java docs for their
information

System Class Java Docs -> http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/System.html
